reviewText: This falls into the "better than nothing" category and should rightly be five bucks or less.  The transfer is really low quality: low resolution, flickering, and dim.  I actually think the copy I downloaded from youtube is superior.  This is the second Asterix DVD I've purchased and they've both been sub-par in terms of video quality.  I would really love to see the Asterix catalog get a proper DVD treatment, but until that happens I guess I'll make do with these half-baked offerings.
